node.text: I met this 18 year old cat (Paris) tonight and got to help take care of her by giving her sub q fluids. I really actually love giving cats Sub q fluids because they have that migrating pancake of fluids under their skin for a while which makes them look all buff on one side. 😂 Anyway París is rickety and old and mostly just bones  and she’s everything I aspire to be. @pewpqueen
